      "content": "it doesn't feel like that though. people here dont even look at me when i walk past. it's not even like i'm missed, i'm just... a ghost. honestly, the only time i feel a bit of relief is when i think about just fading out completely. like, if i just vanished, it would be so quiet and peaceful. no more trying to force myself to fit in somewhere i dont belong.",
